00:49:00,626 --> 00:49:03,126
When is Mom coming back?

391
00:49:09,917 --> 00:49:11,292
Mama...

392
00:49:17,042 --> 00:49:18,917
Your mother... She will...

393
00:49:19,709 --> 00:49:23,334
