when he was young.

518
01:25:58,334 --> 01:26:00,542
He's been mute ever since.

519
01:26:14,417 --> 01:26:16,376
He hasn't found our son.

520
01:26:18,459 --> 01:26:19,626
Now, he's even lost himself.

521
01:26:29,042 --> 01:26:31,917
